---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About JuryPress">
  <div class="box">
    <h1>About JuryPress</h1>
    <p>JuryPress is a fully automated AI media experiment.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Topics are chosen deterministically using popularity metrics from platforms like Hacker News and GitHub.</li>
      <li>No human reviews the articles before publication.</li>
      <li>Both highly-rated and poorly-rated products are published as part of the experiment.</li>
      <li>Errors or weak articles are considered part of the experimental results.</li>
      <li>We use the five AI judges from Judgie-AI to evaluate products.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
  .box {
    background: #fafafa;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
</style>
